| essql 
  query="SELECT AVG(event.duration_ms)/1000 as duration_average FROM \"dummy_app*\" WHERE event.event_type='card_render' AND event.card_id='welcome_card' AND  event.app_timestamp > NOW() - INTERVAL 5 MINUTES"
| math "duration_average"
| formatnumber "0,0.00"
| metric "Welcome" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=48 align="left" color="#000000" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false} 
  labelFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=16 align="left" color="#000000" weight="bold" underline=false italic=false}
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT HISTOGRAM(event.app_timestamp, INTERVAL 10 SECONDS) AS thehistogram, AVG(event.duration_ms)/1000 AS duration FROM \"dummy_app*\" WHERE event.event_type='card_render' AND event.card_id='welcome_card' AND event.app_timestamp > NOW() - INTERVAL 5 MINUTES GROUP BY thehistogram LIMIT 29"
| pointseries x="thehistogram" y="mean(duration)"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle lines=2 fill=1} xaxis=false yaxis=false palette={palette "#e20074" "#531E3A" gradient=false}
| render
